                                <Image Source="https://d338t8kmirgyke.cloudfront.net/icons/icon_pngs/000/004/499/original/good.png" HeightRequest="40"/>
                                <Label Text="Time-traveling, wow, wouldn't it be great if that actually exist? Yeah, we all have some times in the past that we would like to change, but here he is, Mr. Reynolds, to show us how negative consequences that can bring if everyone could change the past."  TextColor="DarkBlue" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
