                                <Label Text="One of the funniest scenes is when Laura(big Adam's lost girlfriend) meets both of them and young Adam immediately crushes on his 'future' girlfriend."  TextColor="DarkBlue" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
